---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { profile } from '../data/profile';
---

<Layout title="About & Leadership">
    <section class="about-hero">
        <h1>About & Leadership</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Engineering Manager | Strategic Leader | AI Innovator</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mission">
        <h2>Mission</h2>
        <p>
            My mission is to build and scale high-performing engineering teams that deliver exceptional value through technical excellence and strategic alignment. With over 9 years of experience, I bridge the gap between complex technical challenges and business objectives, fostering an environment where innovation and efficiency coexist.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="leadership-philosophy">
        <h2>Leadership Philosophy</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Empowerment</h3>
                <p>I believe in hiring great people and giving them the autonomy, tools, and support they need to succeed. Leadership is about removing roadblocks, not micromanagement.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Continuous Excellence</h3>
                <p>From TDD and clean architecture to modern CI/CD, I advocate for high engineering standards that ensure long-term maintainability and system reliability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="value-card">
                <h3>Adaptability</h3>
                <p>In a rapidly evolving landscape—now accelerated by Agentic AI—the ability to pivot and integrate new frameworks is what separates surviving teams from thriving ones.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="technical-leadership">
        <h2>Technical Leadership</h2>
        <p>
            My leadership approach is grounded in a deep technical foundation across the full stack. I specialize in:
        </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Legacy Evolution:</strong> Strategically migrating monolithic systems to modern, containerized architectures (Docker, AWS).</li>
            <li><strong>Engineering Velocity:</strong> Optimizing development lifecycles through automated workflows and AI-assisted coding frameworks.</li>
            <li><strong>Agile Delivery:</strong> Directing cross-functional teams to deliver enterprise-grade features on time and within budget.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="team-building">
        <h2>Team Building</h2>
        <p>
            I currently manage a team of 6+ software engineers at Paycom, where I focus on technical coaching, career development, and building a culture of mutual respect and shared ownership. I believe a team's strength lies in its diversity of thought and its ability to communicate openly.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="beyond-code">
        <h2>Beyond the Code</h2>
        <p>
            When I'm not leading engineering initiatives, I explore the intersection of LLMs and developer productivity. Based in Frisco, Texas, I am an advocate for the local tech community and a lifelong learner, originally holding a degree in Mechanical Engineering from Texas A&M University.
        </p>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    section { margin-top: 5rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 3.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; font-weight: 800; }
    .subtitle { font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--secondary-text); margin-bottom: 2rem; font-weight: 500; }
    
    h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    
    p { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-color); opacity: 0.9; max-width: 800px; }
    
    .values-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .values-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
    }

    .value-card {
        background: var(--card-bg);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }

    .value-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent-color); }

    .value-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--accent-color); }
    .value-card p { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

    ul { margin-top: 1.5rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; }
    li { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-color); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; opacity: 0.9; }
    li strong { color: var(--accent-color); }
</style>
